comments: O'Neale (UTA) briefly places his hand to Parker's (ATL) arm, but immediately slides his hand off disengaging from Parker.
Parker (ATL) splits his feet in the post as he begins his dribble.
Gobert (UTA) has his hand slightly extended but the contact is marginal on the play to the basket by Parker (ATL).
Parker (ATL) is in the paint for less than three seconds when he is imminently actively guarding an opponent.
Reddish (ATL) reaches across Mitchell's (UTA) body and delivers contact to Mitchell's front causing Mitchell to lose control of the ball.
Young (ATL) makes marginal contact with Ingles (UTA) during his driving shot attempt.
Young (ATL) moves alongside of Ingles (UTA) during his drive as the two come together at the end of Ingles' drive without Young delivering contact.
Parker (ATL) steps into Gobert (UTA) delivering body contact that affects Gobert's shot attempt near the rim.
O'Neale (UTA) briefly places his hand to Parker's (ATL) arm, but immediately disengages sliding his hand off.
Huerter (UTA) draws Gobert (ATL) into the air towards him and the contact affects his jump shot attempt.
During the shot attempt near the rim, Len (ATL) has his right arm remain vertical and does not jump through Gobert (UTA) as Gobert is able to attempt his shot.
Len (ATL) briefly has his hand placed to Gobert's (UTA) right arm during the loose ball, but disengages sliding his hand off as Gobert is able to retrieve the loose ball.
Huerter (ATL) briefly places his hand to Mitchell's (UTA) front at the start of the drive, but he moves through the contact and continues his path to the basket.
Len (ATL) jumps from point A to point B and makes contact with Mitchell (UTA) that affects his driving shot attempt.
Gobert (UTA) jumps legally alongside of Hunter (ATL) not delivering contact as his right arm remains collapsed against his body and cleanly blocks the shot with his left hand.
Parker (ATL) commits a take foul on Gobert (UTA).
O'Neale (UTA) maintains a legal guarding position during the jump shot attempt by Young (ATL).
Parker (ATL) commits a take foul on Gobert (UTA).
